    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Scroll of Pass Without Trace</strong> (Level 2 Abjuration)</p><p>A veil of shadows and silence radiates from you, masking you and your companions from detection. For the duration, each creature you choose within 30 feet of you (including you) has a +10 bonus to Dexterity (Stealth) checks and can't be tracked except by magical means. A creature that receives this bonus leaves behind no tracks or other traces of its passage.</p><p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S, M (Ashes from a burned leaf of mistletoe and a sprig of spruce.)</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action | <strong>Range:</strong> Self | <strong>Duration:</strong> Up to 1 hour (Concentration)</p><p><em>Classes: Druid, Ranger</em></p>",
